A state of melting with romance
====================================
The feeling of romance is state of heart, we feel romantic at the last state, before to this state our heart stream a certain period of time towards romance.
This is nothing but the matching of our heart frequency with others/self/nature/activity of others frequencies.

Every things have certain frequency having certain web length with it. Heart have also some frequency and web length. If energy in heart increase the intensity of same frequency
increase, in other word state of frequency change their state and it come in such a state it is able to match with others frequencies.

Fist of all your heart frequency already in higher state and other thing it match with others frequencies, due to matching of frequencies, your heart frequency increase and their
web length increase and finally you feel to much more romantic.

If you supply more and more energy to your self, you heart frequency change their state with supply energy.
It reach to many state and realize many things in different manner.

***Neither to support nor to oppose the healing, just be with it***

Due to continuous supply of energy/meditation your heart come in such a state and it heal in such a manner that the thinking of mind is almost in disappear mode.
This  is nothing but the state of melting with romance.
At this state even the light observation change the state of romance.

***Romance with self is much more costly than with others***

In this state, you unable to configure, you are in romance or romance is in you.
You unable to configure/distinguish, you are listening a romantic songs or you only singing or the frequency of songs is you only.

If you try to distinguish/configure the above state, you realize the intensity of romance decrease.

***Neither to configure/distinguish nor to try anyways just be with streaming***
***Romance is highly paid in its nature, doesn't matter it is with self or others***

